skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cat lover
des: A must have for any cat, or dog lover. Facts, Jokes, Sounds, and more. I can meow, purr, and bark. I also have angry, chirp, strange, and whine meow sounds. Most sounds have multiple files. Hours of enjoyment watching your animal respond to the disembodied cat or dog.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
